            "title": "泡泡龍講投資│市況波動勿用槓桿（泡泡龍）",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"其實呢種市況，已經進入超高波動時間。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/k2QDpUL0qovEFUJx57YyuQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2024-09/a055c290-8126-11ef-bf3e-9c6e91c1c84d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">其實呢種市況，已經進入超高波動時間。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">很遺憾同大家講，今篇專欄會係筆者係Yahoo最後一篇文章，都好榮幸見證Yahoo財經起起伏伏，潮起潮落，緣聚終有時！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-yga='{\"yLinkPosition\":\"1\",\"yLinkElement\":\"affiliate_link\",\"yAffiliateService\":\"other\",\"yPosition\":\"1\",\"yModuleName\":\"shop-now\",\"ySellerName\":\"Yahoo\",\"yLinkText\":\"下載Yahoo財經APP\",\"yHasCommerce\":true}' data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">講番美股市場，呢排個市簡直係玩死人系列。上星期五又再次黑色星期五，特別係收到美國出兵攻打伊朗，要打爆伊朗發電設施。雖然設施未打到，但個市已經被打倒！納指大跌3%以上。而在星期一，繼續承接上星期五跌勢，係亞洲時段進入恐慌時間，然後，大約香港時間晚上7點左右，Trump一句說話，又改變世界，又話同伊朗有傾計，仲要話進展良好！個市即刻大彈，不過之後又傳出伊朗否認。筆者都好想講句粗口，完全唔知邊個講真話，但股市就好似被人造市咁，大升大跌！</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dd372a41-b348-4bee-b69c-15078cc45e29-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其實呢種市況，已經進入超高波動時間，任何一個言論，可以令個股上落5%至10%，所以容錯率好低，而且極端市況風險都愈來愈大，所以唔太適合重倉投資，因為一旦場面失控，損失將會極大。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">咁你話個市見底未呢？坦白講，筆者就覺得未見底，似乎最近既反彈似係大跌浪中嘅小反彈。除非美國真係同伊朗傾好數，願意停火。如果唔係，都只係視為市場noise 。因為呢類言論，可以短期抒緩市場擔憂情緒，但對實際情況無任何幫助，海峽仍然未通，油價仍然高企，通脹重燃機會仍然大增。這也是為甚麼黃金白銀近期大跌原因，市場已經由炒今年減息轉為炒今年加息，是完全不一樣既前景。真係天堂轉為地獄！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">筆者再次提醒大家，現在真係唔好用槓桿，又或者玩槓桿產品，因為好容易輸身家。投資不是賭博，唔需要每一局都參與，現時市況係極高難度，都係人為市，好容易大上大落被震走，倒不如抽身遠離股市，放鬆一下心情，等市況明朗，調整好自己狀態再參與更好！到時相信賺錢將會更輕鬆！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最後，祝Yahoo 讀者今年投資最終逢凶化吉轉危為機，賺到盆滿缽滿！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">泡泡龍</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本欄逢周三刊出</p></div>",
